summary: I have never suffered from any type of mental health issues. Yeah, sometimes I have bad days, but everyone does and I’ve never...
body:
I have never suffered from any type of mental health issues. Yeah, sometimes I have bad days, but everyone does and I’ve never really thought about how much a thing like depression or OCD or anything really would effect anyone’s lives. I had sympathy and support for them but I never knew how bad it was

That is until Dan’s depression video

This video opened my eyes about mental health and I knew I had to do more to help those it does effect. Last year during my senior year, I was in the child care program at my school, and we had to teach them something important going forward into life. I decided to teach them about mental health, inspired by Dan’s video because if we can catch it when they are young we can help them right away and teach little kids to have empathy for people right away. I also donated money to Young Minds in support. All of this because Dan posted one video on the internet. Dan is much more than just an average person on YouTube, he inspires and he helps heal people. If you are able to support Dan, support him and support Young Minds. If you have any mental health issues stay strong because you are loved and valid and to anyone who doesn’t, reach out to people who do and try to help in any way you can. @danielhowell stay caring and loving, you are more important than you know💕

summary: I love Dan so much. I literally do not trust anyone who say they don’t like him. He has such a genuine, pure, kind and gentle...
body: I love Dan so much. I literally do not trust anyone who say they don’t like him. He has such a genuine, pure, kind and gentle heart that wants to help people. Seriously, you don’t see any other YouTuber helping people the way Dan does. I am so, so proud of him for telling us about his depression, even more proud of him for pushing through it and the absolute most proud that he is helping and trying to inspire others to overcome their mental health issues as well. I’m sending my love to Dan and everyone else in the world who needs it today💛💛💛💛💛

Thank you for releasing ‘Daniel and Depression’. Thank you for trusting the Phandom with this part of your life. Thank you for helping me stay alive for years.
